///////////////////////////////
    Component
////////////////////////////
Functional                       |          Class Base
---------------------------------------------------------------
Dumb Component,                  |    Logical Component
ProjectionComponent,             |
Display Component                |
                                 |
Light in weight                  | Heavy as compare to Functional
It cannot maintain State         | It Can maintain State


---------
State => Act like local variable
Props => use to pass state from one component to another


Component A      ====>         Component B 
state1           props          State2


